 155:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****  ===============================================================================
 156:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****              ##### Initialization and de-initialization Functions  #####
 157:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****  ===============================================================================
 158:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****     [..]
 159:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       This section provides functions allowing to initialize and de-initialize the
 160:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       RAMCFG instance.
 161:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****     [..]
 162:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_Init() function follows the RAMCFG instance configuration
 163:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       procedures as described in the reference manual.
 164:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_DeInit() function allows to deinitialize the RAMCFG instance.
 165:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       HAL_RAMCFG_Init() and HAL_RAMCFG_DeInit() APIs do not change the activation
 166:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       status of ECC feature. It is managed by HAL_RAMCFG_StartECC(),
 167:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       HAL_RAMCFG_StopECC() or option bytes (When available on the device).
 168:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c **** 
 169:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c **** @endverbatim
 170:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****   * @{
 171:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****   */
 172:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c **** 
