 314:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****                       ##### ECC Operations Functions  #####
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccHXHETX.s 			page 11


 315:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****  ===============================================================================
 316:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****     [..]
 317:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       This section provides functions allowing to manage ECC feature provided by
 318:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       the RAMCFG peripheral.
 319:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****     [..]
 320:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_StartECC() function allows starting the ECC mechanism and
 321:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       enabling ECC address latching for the selected RAMCFG instance.
 322:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_StopECC() function allows stopping the ECC mechanism and
 323:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       disabling ECC address latching for the selected RAMCFG instance.
 324:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_EnableNotification() function allows enabling interrupts
 325:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       for single ECC error, double ECC error and NMI error.
 326:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_DisableNotification() function allows disabling interrupts
 327:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       for single ECC error, double ECC error. When NMI interrupt is enabled it
 328:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       can only be disabled by a global peripheral reset or by a system reset.
 329:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_IsECCSingleErrorDetected() function allows to check if an
 330:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       single ECC error has occurred.
 331:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_IsECCDoubleErrorDetected() function allows to check if an
 332:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       double ECC error has occurred.
 333:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_GetSingleErrorAddress() function allows to get the address of
 334:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       the last single ECC error detected.
 335:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       The HAL_RAMCFG_GetDoubleErrorAddress() function allows to get the address of
 336:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c ****       the last double ECC error detected.
 337:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c **** 
 338:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ramcfg.c **** @endverbatim
